sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CMReconciler as ConfigMap Reconciler
    participant Config as Config Object<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9090/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant SatEngine as Saturation Engine<br/>(V1/V2/QueueModel)
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant VAReconciler as VA Reconciler
    participant Actuator as Actuator<br/>/metrics 8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPAKEDA as HPA / KEDA
    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant SFZEngine as Scale-from-Zero<br/>Engine
    participant DirectAct as DirectActuator
    participant ScaleTarget as Deployment /<br/>LeaderWorkerSet

    Note over User,ScaleTarget: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling (every 30s)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create VariantAutoscaling CR
    K8sAPI->>VAReconciler: Watch event (VA created)

    loop Every 30s optimization cycle
        SatEngine->>Prom: PromQL: vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc,<br/>num_requests_waiting, token rates<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>SatEngine: Per-replica metrics
        SatEngine->>SatEngine: Run saturation analysis<br/>(V1 percentage / V2 token / QueueModel)
        SatEngine->>Cache: Store scaling decision<br/>(desired replicas per VA)
        Cache->>VAReconciler: Channel trigger (requeue)
    end

    VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Patch VA status<br/>(optimal allocation)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    SatEngine->>Actuator: Update Prometheus gauges
    Note over Actuator: wva_desired_replicas<br/>wva_current_replicas<br/>wva_desired_ratio
    HPAKEDA->>Actuator: GET /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Actuator-->>HPAKEDA: Scaling metrics
    HPAKEDA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI->>ScaleTarget: Update replicas

    Note over User,ScaleTarget: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero (every 100ms)

    loop Every 100ms polling cycle
        SFZEngine->>EPP: Scrape flow_control_queue_size<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (epp-metrics-token)
        EPP-->>SFZEngine: Queue size metrics
        alt Pending requests for dormant model
            SFZEngine->>K8sAPI: PATCH scale subresource<br/>(replicas: 0 → 1)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
            K8sAPI->>ScaleTarget: Direct scale-up
            SFZEngine->>Cache: Store scale-from-zero decision
            Cache->>VAReconciler: Channel trigger
            VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Patch VA status
        end
    end

    Note over User,ScaleTarget: Flow 3: ConfigMap Configuration

    K8sAPI->>CMReconciler: ConfigMap watch event
    CMReconciler->>Config: Update scaling parameters<br/>(saturation thresholds,<br/>per-model tuning)
    Config-->>SatEngine: Applied on next<br/>optimization cycle
